### ============================================================================
### CREDITS — /api/v1/credits + /api/v1/user-credit-plans + /api/v1/credit-requests
### ============================================================================

### ─── Credits ───────────────────────────────────────────────

### List my credits (paginated, optional companyId)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/credits?companyId={{companyId}}&page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get credit by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/credits/{{purchaseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### ─── Credit Plans ──────────────────────────────────────────

### List credit plans
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/user-credit-plans?companyId={{companyId}}

### Get credit plan by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/user-credit-plans/{{creditPlanId}}

### Create custom credit plan
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/user-credit-plans/custom
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyId": {{companyId}},
  "credits": 500,
  "pricePerCredit": 150.00,
  "currency": "NGN",
  "description": "Custom plan for Acme Corp"
}

### ─── Credit Requests ───────────────────────────────────────

### List credit requests (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/credit-requests?companyId={{companyId}}&page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get credit request by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/credit-requests/{{creditRequestId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Create credit request
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/credit-requests
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "creditsRequested": 30,
  "reason": "Need additional credits for upcoming business trip",
  "companyId": {{companyId}},
  "employeeId": {{employeeId}}
}

### Update credit request
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/credit-requests/{{creditRequestId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "creditsRequested": 50,
  "reason": "Updated: Need more credits"
}

### Approve credit request
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/credit-requests/{{creditRequestId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Reject credit request
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/credit-requests/{{creditRequestId}}/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Insufficient budget this quarter"
}

### Delete credit request
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/credit-requests/{{creditRequestId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
